      "description": "Affordable and approachable, this vehicle is a practical option for buyers seeking basic transportation or a solid project at a budget-conscious price. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values straightforward utility over cosmetics, but it still offers real potential and everyday usefulness for the right owner. A smart low-cost opportunity to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget.",
