    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride with plenty of life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts conversations for all the right reasons: affordable entry point, dependable basics, and a great option for someone who wants simple transportation or a project to tinker with. If you\u2019re realistic and want solid value without spending a fortune, this one could be a great fit. Priced to move and worth a look.",
