    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward project with solid bones and plenty of usable mechanical value. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it offers a great starting point for someone looking for an affordable driver, tuner base, or weekend rehab candidate. Cosmetically it shows its age and needs attention, but for the money you\u2019re getting a complete vehicle with real upside and a lot of serviceable hardware. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
