    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with honest character and plenty of story left to tell. It\u2019s the kind of ride that turns heads not because it\u2019s trying too hard, but because it has that rare, lived-in presence\u2014perfect for someone who appreciates a practical set of wheels with personality. Whether you need an inexpensive daily, a weekend project, or a dependable backup to keep life moving, this one offers a great entry point and the chance to make it your own. Affordable, full of potential, and ready for its next chapter.",
